{"tid":810483,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《逆流大叔》原班底添食","createTime":"2018-09-08T04:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:41:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"138bc8025e4575d4482fe8f901f6898947fa7d86","tid":810483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180908/20494599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180908%2F20494599&d=9xv0JFbQRmkqdytgjbZEH54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=deebef3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180908%2F20494599&h=3d74a92e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180908/20494599</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月08日 <br />\n<br />\n《逆流大叔》原班底添食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180908/large/08ec4p15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180908%2Flarge%2F08ec4p15.jpg&h=083be7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡子彤（左）和導演陳詠燊昨日在商台宣傳電影《逆流大叔》，對於電影已經有接近1,300萬票房，陳詠燊表示感謝觀眾與傳媒支持：「計劃緊原班人馬再拍，但唔係短期內嘅事。」問到會否開拍《逆流大嬸》？他笑言胡定欣一定不會放過自己。提到黃德斌結婚，他們表示未有準備送禮，因為黃德斌太低調。對於女友歐鎧淳為運動員發聲，但被指別有用心，胡子彤說：「佢冇唔開心，都係分享自己感受。」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n歌神開心度70歲大壽<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n沈震軒預告旺角玩快閃"},{"pid":"29caf2a47f92eab2464e22b8f8718a991f17c2e8","tid":810483,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"余香凝又有job"},{"pid":"b50df052e0f1bed16a1cc457bc14d3297503638a","tid":810483,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"鎮宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔收錢<img src=\"/assets/fa